    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><h5 id="1个vercel账号，1个github账号，Vscode-Git"><a href="#1个vercel账号，1个github账号，Vscode-Git" class="headerlink" title="1个vercel账号，1个github账号，Vscode,Git"></a>1个vercel账号，1个github账号，Vscode,Git</h5><h2 id="部署Hexo"><a href="#部署Hexo" class="headerlink" title="部署Hexo"></a>部署Hexo</h2><h5 id="1-新建一个文件夹，右键打开Git-Bash-输入"><a href="#1-新建一个文件夹，右键打开Git-Bash-输入" class="headerlink" title="1.新建一个文件夹，右键打开Git Bash,输入"></a>1.新建一个文件夹，右键打开Git Bash,输入</h5><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">hexo init [blogroot]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> [blogroot]</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
